<% canonical = @canonical_slug ? "https://smarts.md/#{@canonical_slug}" : "https://smarts.md/#{@chain.slug}/#{@contract.address}" %>
<% reference = @canonical_slug || "#{@chain.slug}/#{@contract.address}" %>
<% explorer = explorer_address_url(@chain, @contract.address) %>
# <%= contract_display_name %> on <%= @chain.name %>

- **Address:** `<%= @contract.address %>`
- **Chain:** <%= @chain.name %>
<% if @classification %>
- **Classification:** <%= @classification.display_name %>
<% end %>
<% if @contract.compiler_version.present? %>
- **Compiler:** Solidity <%= @contract.compiler_version %>
<% end %>
<% if @contract.license.present? %>
- **License:** <%= @contract.license %>
<% end %>
<% if @contract.implementation_address.present? %>
- **Proxy implementation:** `<%= @contract.implementation_address %>`
<% end %>

<% if @classification&.description.present? %>
_<%= @classification.description %>_

<% end %>
## Query via AI agent

- **MCP endpoint:** `https://smarts.md/mcp`
- **Reference:** `<%= reference %>`
- **Sample prompt:** "Tell me the current state of <%= reference %>"

Setup for Claude Code, Cursor, Windsurf, Cline: <https://mcp.smarts.md/>
<% if @protocol_adapter %>

<%= render @protocol_adapter.template_partial, adapter: @protocol_adapter %>
<% end %>

## Admin & Risk

<% if @admin_risk&.error.present? %>
Could not build admin risk profile: <%= @admin_risk.error %>
<% elsif @admin_risk %>
<%= @admin_risk.summary %>

<% if @admin_risk.risk_flags.any? %>
- **Detected controls:** <%= @admin_risk.risk_flags.map { |flag| admin_risk_flag_label(flag) }.join(", ") %>
<% end %>
<% if @admin_risk.controls.any? %>
- **Current controls:**
<% @admin_risk.controls.each do |control| %>
  - <%= control[:label] %>: `<%= admin_risk_value(control) %>`
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% if @admin_risk.recent_governance[:count].to_i.positive? %>
- **Governance events loaded:** <%= @admin_risk.recent_governance[:count] %><% if @admin_risk.recent_governance[:latest_event] %> (latest: `<%= @admin_risk.recent_governance[:latest_event] %>` at block `<%= @admin_risk.recent_governance[:latest_block] || "unknown" %>`)<% end %>
<% end %>
<% if @admin_risk.warnings.any? %>
<% @admin_risk.warnings.each do |warning| %>
- _Note:_ <%= warning %>
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% else %>
No admin risk profile available.
<% end %>

## Recent activity

<% if @activity&.error.present? %>
Could not load recent activity: <%= @activity.error %>
<% elsif @activity&.events.present? %>
Decoded from the verified ABI, newest first.
<% if @activity.event_filter.present? %>
Filter: `<%= @activity.event_filter %>`
<% end %>
<% if @activity.latest_block %>
Window: blocks `<%= @activity.from_block %>` → `<%= @activity.latest_block %>`
<% end %>

<% @activity.events.first(10).each do |event| %>
- **<%= event.event %>** at block `<%= event.block_number || "unknown" %>`<% if event.tx_hash.present? %>, tx `<%= event.tx_hash %>`<% end %><% if (summary = activity_event_summary(event)) %> — <%= summary %><% end %>
<% if event.unknown? %>
  - topic0: `<%= event.topic0 || "unknown" %>`
<% elsif event.args.present? %>
<% event.args.each do |key, value| %>
  - <%= format_activity_arg(key.presence || "arg") %>: `<%= format_activity_arg(value) %>`
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

Ask your AI agent: "<%= activity_prompt(reference) %>"
<% else %>
No recent events found in the current block window.
<% end %>

## Governance timeline

<% if @governance&.error.present? && @governance.events.blank? %>
Could not load governance timeline: <%= @governance.error %>
<% elsif @governance&.events.present? %>
Privileged events only — role changes, proxy upgrades, pauses, blacklisting, minter config. Newest first.
<% if @governance.latest_block %>
Scanned through block `<%= @governance.latest_block %>`.
<% end %>

<%
  by_category = @governance.events.group_by(&:category)
  GovernanceEvent::CATEGORIES.each do |cat|
    next unless by_category[cat]&.any?
%>
### <%= governance_category_label(cat) %> (<%= by_category[cat].size %>)

<% by_category[cat].first(10).each do |event| %>
- **<%= event.event_name %>** at block `<%= event.block_number %>`<% if event.block_timestamp %>, <%= event.block_timestamp.iso8601 %><% end %><% if event.tx_hash.present? %>, tx `<%= event.tx_hash %>`<% end %>
<% if event.summary.present? %>
  - <%= event.summary %>
<% end %>
<% end %>
<% if by_category[cat].size > 10 %>
- _… <%= by_category[cat].size - 10 %> more_
<% end %>

<% end %>
Ask your AI agent: "Show me how admin power has evolved on <%= reference %> — who held which role when, and what's changed in the past year."
<% else %>
No governance events recorded in the recent window. This contract may be fully autonomous, or no admin actions have occurred recently.
<% end %>

## Links

- Docs: <<%= canonical %>>
<% if explorer %>
- <%= explorer_name(@chain) %>: <<%= explorer %>>
<% end %>
